{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2eb96897f9","title":"关于审查藏文广播问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4dfd82fb60","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":13,"articleId":"2eb96897f9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"94686d610b","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2eb96897f9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在中共中央西南局1950年5月3日关于转报甘孜情报站的情况给中央的报告上的批语。甘孜情报站的报告中说：有藏人反映，北京藏语广播曾播出“西藏人民系受神权与贵族双重压道，我们决来解放你们”这样的话。如果以武力解决西藏问题，这样说是可以的。否则，不必如此，特别是在西藏又具向内之心的情况下，应争取达赖。如此，则解放西藏可收事半功倍之效。"},{"id":"3b821bc06a","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2eb96897f9","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李维汉（1896-1984），又名罗迈，湖南长沙人。当时任中共中央统战部部长、中央人民政府民族事务委员会主任委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a38bc48c43","type":"title","text":"关于审香藏文广播问题","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2eb96897f9"},{"id":"94686d610b","type":"paragraph","text":"请季维汉负责审香藏文广播并规定该项广播内容及方针。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2eb96897f9"},{"id":"3b821bc06a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2eb96897f9"},{"id":"d4b65651b4","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十三日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2eb96897f9"}],"page":{"id":"c7001e7ae9","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2eb96897f9","start":388,"end":388}}}},"__N_SSG":true}